E1E3AUD.original: ~z~We got cops coming up the rear.
~z~Johnny, I need you to take out the windows of that showroom, aight?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，你给我把展厅的玻璃打烂，懂？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~What? You been stepping on this shit?
~z~I don't know about you, but I ain't got a clean record, so drive!
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~不清楚你的底细，反正我底子不干净，快开车！

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Did he? We all gotta die sometime, Johnny. Give Malc my condolences, okay?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~是吗？人终有一死，Johnny。替我安慰下Malc，好吗？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~So what you going do about it?
~z~I know what it feels like to lose a brother, friend. Call me if you need anything. So long.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~我知道失去兄弟的痛苦，朋友。有需要就联系我。再见。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Cops got us in the spot for real, now.
~z~Alright Jonathan, what is it this time?
~z~Hey. Check the LCPD Patriots up ahead.
~z~Andreas, you piece of shit, leave the girl alone. She knows how I like it.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~Andreas，傻逼儿子，别再多嘴了。她知道我的口味。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~We surrounded by dirty ass coppers here.
~z~Man, you drive like you live - insane!
~z~Good thing he's driving a car and not riding a bike.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~幸好他开的是警车，不是摩托。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Exchanges aren't ever simple in this city. Wouldn't be fun if they were. See you soon.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~从来没有简单的交易。简单就没意思了。一会儿见。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Come on, Terry, take out the pigs.
~z~I hope they can walk away from that one.
~z~Yo, yo! We got cops in the sky look out, Johnny.
~z~You don't need to tell her shit... leave my...
~z~We ain't nowhere. Shit's fucked, Liz. There ain't no operating in this town. I'm sorry.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~走不了了，全他妈完了，Liz。现在不会有什么交易了，抱歉。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Listen, you do your job... and let us do ours.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~听着，你们只管送货...验货交给我们。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Ha, ha, ha and you know that's gotta hurt.
~z~Come on, let's get out of here!
~z~Shit, Johnny. We got a bird in the sky.
~z~You a maniac Johnny, it's good, it's good.
~z~-Yo, you see what you did? This shit's fucked up man!~n~-Fuck!
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~－哟，看看你做了什么？全他妈吹了，伙计！~n~－操！

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~I think we lost the last of the heat, boys.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~刚才应该是最后一波条子了，各位。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You got health insurance, man, I don't.
~z~Eyes behind us, Johnny. We got cops on us.
~z~Shit. They got Patriots blocking the road.
~z~Let's do this! Uptown Riders featuring The Lost in a Bohan joint, baby.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~上路吧！上城骑士携手失落帮，加入Bohan监狱，宝贝。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You drive like a lunatic! I like it.
~z~We got to head up to Butterfly. This shit is going down up there.
~z~-God damn you motherfuckers!~n~-Gonna need that shit.
~z~Johnny. How'd it go? Do I have some bail money at least.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，怎么样了？我的保释金有着落了吗？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Man, oh, man. This shit is heavy.
~z~How you like the feel of this, Johnny?
~z~Ahh shit. Five-o's right on top of us, man.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~我操，条子在我们头顶上，兄弟。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Put a fork in him, he's done.
~z~Get the cops off our ass, Terry.
~z~I got a feeling we're not gonna get away from these cops.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~我觉得这下很难逃出条子的魔爪了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Maybe we should get us a room together at the Jefferson Motel?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~要么我们去杰佛森汽车旅馆开个房间吧？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Shit man, DeSean. Knew that motherfucker since diapers. That shit ain't right.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，DeSean。从小在一块儿的兄弟。这他妈不对啊。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Maybe you guys should get rid of him and sell this coke later. Huh?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~要么你们先干掉他，晚点再去卖可卡因？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~How we gonna get out of this one?
~z~What up kid, I got that package for you.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你好吗，小子，货给你送过来了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Come on, get us out of here.
~z~No time for tyre kicking. You guys will get to know each other soon enough.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~没时间开玩笑了。你们马上就会熟络起来的。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Don't fucking listen to me. I'm just making shit up as I go along, baby.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~听不懂别听。走到哪里扯到哪里而已，宝贝。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~We making this transaction on them courts up on Butterfly. Come on.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~交易地点在Butterfly街的篮球场。走吧。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Terrence, man, the pigs are closing in.
~z~Deal didn't happen. Buyer got smart. Pigs got involved. Our friends're heading back with the product.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~交易吹了。买家想逃单，条子出现了。我们的朋友带着货回来了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Ahhh, always space for you, Johnny boy.
~z~I gotta say, I haven't seen Liz Torres that crazy before.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~只能说，我从没见Liz Torres那么疯狂过。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Keep the cops off our back, fellas.
~z~So you should be, you know. So you should be.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你确实该抱歉好吧。哈，确实该抱歉。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't got time for chit chat. You boys'll get along.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~没时间拉家常了，你们能处得来。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Cops be rushing us from the left, boy.
~z~I'm going to take it for our own.
~z~We ain't gotta worry bout that cop no more.
~z~Shit, DeSean. What the fuck are you doing?
~z~Look after her until the heat's gone?
~z~Nah, nah, nah. We gotta go. Shit's gotta get done.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~不不不不不，我们要走了。有正事要干。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~I think you might wanna look right.
~z~You best count yourself lucky you still here. Bye bye, Johnny.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你还活着，运气算不错了。拜拜，Johnny。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~I ain't into the whole jail thing.
~z~Aight, we gotta head out to the courts on Butterfly. Let's go.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~好了，我们要去Butterfly街的篮球场。走吧。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Thanks for makin' room on that pussy pad.
~z~Things couldn't get much worse here, you know. You know these is tough times.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~这已经是糟糕透顶了，日子真是难过啊。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~That's what the fuck I'm talking about!
~z~and you need someone to hold your little hand. We'll be there.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~需要有人牵着你的小手手。待会儿就来。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Cops to the left. Do somethin' about it, Man.
~z~They got their eyes in the sky on us, man.
~z~Smash them cherry tops, Clay. Come on.
~z~Do you want us to take Marta off your hands?
~z~Seems like these cops have got us surrounded.
~z~Shit, I'd be good to go if I had some cooch like that.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，要是有个那么好的小妞，我也跟她一样暴躁。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Well, you best change your mindset, 'cause this right here man, is happening.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~那你们最好改改主意，货没了就是没了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Lost MC. Uptown Riders. Let's fucking do it.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~失落帮，上城骑士。一起开干吧。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Come on, drive Johnny, drive you punk!
~z~Shit now it's cops on the right, Johnny. Do what you gotta do.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，条子现在在右边。该干嘛干嘛。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~I think that shit is gonna blow!
~z~Shit. It wouldn't be a war on drugs if there weren't victims, you know.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的。要是不会死人就不叫毒品战争了，对吧？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Gas is really gonna get expensive now.
~z~Terry! Clay! Keep the bulls off us.
~z~I always hated these yuppie cars anyway.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~我本来就看这些雅痞车不顺眼。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Yo, B, five-o all up on top of us!
~z~You only got to worry about yourself and selling that coke.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你只需要关心好自己和要卖的可卡因。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You like taking chances, don't you, D?
~z~And don't you don't gotta worry about her neither. Okay?
~z~Man, that shit sure does fall from the sky.
~z~LCPD can't get their own cars to work.
~z~-We gotta take this shit back to Liz.~n~-Right, right.
~z~Coppers all around, B! They all around!
~z~You best stay away from me and Marta for a while. See you.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~最近你最好跟我和Marta保持距离。再见。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~No, I don't think there's gonna be another time man. Shit's closing in.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~不，我看是没机会了，老兄。时日无多了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You ain't getting your hands on my baby girl.
~z~Terry! Clay! Deal with the pigs, men. Come on.
~z~You think there's something going down with Liz and Marta? Shit.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你觉得Liz和Marta之间的关系不纯吗？我操。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Looks like you're on foot now, friend.
~z~I heard you and your brothers liked that hardcore hard rock bonding shit.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~听说你们帮的弟兄喜欢那什么硬核摇滚。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You'd thought you'd cut me in because you're scared shitless
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~你会叫上我是因为你吓出屎了，

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Those are some tax payer dollars gone to waste.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~纳税人的钱都浪费在这儿了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~The fucking bulls are right in front of us.
~z~We need you to get rid of five-o behind us. Use this shit.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~快点把后面的条子干掉。用这个。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Here he is. You want to help him oversee a simple exchange?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~就是我。你想帮我盯一场简单的交易吗？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Shit. They got a helicopter up there.
~z~All these snitches all over the place.
~z~Get the heat away from us, boys.
~z~Here's something heavy, Fam. Take out this heat behind us.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~给你来个大的，家人。解决屁股后面的条子。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~It's pure as punks like you gonna find.
~z~Alright, baby. Just don't get freaked out if you see me rolling in a cop car.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~好的，宝贝。万一看见我坐在警车里，你也别慌。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Shit, pigs don't have no respect for private property.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，条子真不尊重私人财产。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You wanna go to jail homeboy? Drive!
~z~That's right, I'm gonna be waiting for you and you and and anybody else who shows up, ok?
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~确实。你俩我都等着，谁来了我都等着，好吗？

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Hold of this, Johnny. You need to clear these coppers the fuck out.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~拿好了，Johnny。赶紧把那些条子灭了。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~The cops are right in front of us.
~z~Yo, B. You gonna have to take out them showroom windows, now.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~哟，兄。赶紧把展厅玻璃打烂，快！

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~You fucking hear that on your wiretap, Andreas?
~z~That's a case of over steering if ever I saw one.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~这应该就是所谓的转向过猛吧。

E1E3AUD.original: ~z~Things went bad Liz. DeSean had himself an accident.
~z~Weird times call for weird measures, Liz.
~z~Just baby sitting a deal. Piece of cake. Thought I'd cut you in because I like you so much.
E1E3AUD.translated: ~z~照看一笔交易而已，小菜一碟。想叫上你就找你了。
